2️⃣ Type 2 – Cryptic Digit Pattern

Digits are hidden using rules.

Example

If

3 → 18
5 → 50
7 → 98

Then

9 → ?
Solution

Observe pattern

3 × 3 × 2 = 18
5 × 5 × 2 = 50
7 × 7 × 2 = 98

So

9 × 9 × 2 = 162

✅ Answer = 162





