3️⃣ Type 3 – Coding Numbers

Numbers coded with different numbers.

Example

If

123 = 36
234 = 72
345 = 120

Find

456 = ?
Solution

Pattern:

123 → (1+2+3) × 6 = 6×6 = 36
234 → (2+3+4) × 8 = 9×8 = 72
345 → (3+4+5) × 10 = 12×10 = 120

Next

456 → (4+5+6) × 12
= 15 × 12
= 180

✅ Answer = 180




